      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising showroom standard. This unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a machine in pristine condition. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, ensuring an aesthetic and mechanical profile that remains peerless. Inquiries are invited from those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
